parameters: "Victory over Anomalocaris Mosman! Who will be\nthe next enemy...? Chapter"
"Let's go to the Monster Fight Arena!"

Shark Broccoli: Well done, Duke Shark... With Anomalocaris
and dozens of members under our control, we've obtained all
their operations. We're one step closer to our long-
cherished goal of unifying the city...

Memimi: Haha, Boss Shark Broccoli-sama! I'm so happy to
contribute to the dominance of our organization! We must
hurry with the re-education of the members...

Underling: But seriously, who would have thought Duke
Shark's true face was such a beautiful girl... And to think
she was just Samemountain-san from the convenience store. I
thought she was just a struggling student...

Underling: Since the Shark Mask is custom-made, it seems it
will take time to repair. For now, it looks like she'll be
operating without it... Her true identity has spread
throughout the city.

Shark Broccoli: Let's give you your reward... I'll promote
you from the Four Devas to Vice-Leader! Additionally, I'll
grant you gift vouchers worth 100,000 yen to use around the
city...

Underling: Oh... The seat of Vice-Leader, long vacant, has
finally been taken by Duke Shark-sama...! It just shows how
much she has contributed to the organization. It's as if the
successor of the organization has been decided...

Underling: A reward of 100,000 yen! With that much, one
could have a blast in the shopping district in front of the
station... Even at the department stores in the city...
Memimi: What an honor! I humbly accept...!

Memimi: (After exposing myself masturbating naked to
everyone in the city... It's only fair I get some perks...
Hehe... Uh, uhehe...)

Memimi rose to the position of Number 2, being honored for
her achievements in greatly expanding the organization after
defeating Anomalocaris...

Memimi: Hehe... The next Monster Fight has already been
decided. I must go to the venue for a face-to-face
meeting... I'm looking forward to it!
